{"tid":2323614,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（天佑美國）美國破1600萬人確診　單日3309人不治創新高","createTime":"2020-12-13T09:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T06:13:35.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aada968d85ffb686f1db7da16660166d50998e55","tid":2323614,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1948353/即時-國際-美國破1600萬人確診-單日3309人不治創新高\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1948353%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%B41600%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A53309%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=1703a6a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1948353%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%B41600%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A53309%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98&h=4b2e3c05\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1948353/即時-國際-美國破1600萬人確診-單日3309人不治創新高</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國約翰霍普金斯大學數據顯示，全球超過7100萬人確診新冠肺炎，死亡人數突破160萬人，美國仍然是疫情最嚴重的國家，11日新增3309人不治，創單日新高，全國現時超過1600萬人確診，死亡人數逾29萬7500人，直逼30萬大關。<br />\n<br />\n美國也創下單日確診新高紀錄有23萬1775宗，較12月4日創下的先前最高紀錄，多出將近4000宗。<br />\n<br />\n美國食品及藥物管理局昨日通過授權緊急使用輝瑞及德國夥伴研發的疫苗，首批疫苗預計當地星期一(14日)早上，可運送到多州的150個地點，各地醫院，醫院的醫護人員及其他醫療照護人員將優先接種。"},{"pid":"c12f3fbe1713ee62851760e1ba2b828309b28bf3","tid":2323614,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:58:58.000Z","msg":"點解中國係零？"},{"pid":"effc8cad2bd8110da20df0e546e497a54e9bd12c","tid":2323614,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"美國1日死3千幾人，打仗都冇死咁多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db70cb84dc16